  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/07/google-text-to-speech-app-play/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/6c4febb610c07e680970a593acb2a622/google-text-t-speech-available-on-google-play.png\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nAndroid <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2012/09/28/google-play-services-arrives-for-android-2-2-and-above/\">内建应用</a>登陆 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/06/google-stock-android-keyboard-to-play-store/\">Google Play</a> 的趋势仍在继续，这一次上架的是「Google 文字转语音」。这款应用本身虽算不上什么「大腕」，但配合「Google Play 图书」或「Google 翻译」它能「大声朗读」选定的内容给你听。另外，此番 Google 还为其加入了韩语支持，中文嘛，暂时还没什么声音。需要提醒大家的是，至少要 IceCream Sandwich 才能运行这项应用，不过以<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/04/more-than-half-of-android-devices-now-run-jelly-bean/\">最新的统计结果</a>来看，应该不会是什么大问题吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/07/google-text-to-speech-app-play/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://www.phonearena.com/news/Google-releases-Text-to-Speech-into-the-Play-Store_id49117\" target=\"_blank\">Phone Arena</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.tts\" target=\"_blank\">Google Play</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/07/google-text-to-speech-app-play/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20763092/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/07/google-text-to-speech-app-play/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
